{
  "stem": "232.6",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I kind of joined an Italian family with a boy and a daughter and was husband and wife.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I stuck to them because I was all by myself.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Like I said, the train started rolling.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we could look to a little window, where there's barbed wire.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We wanted to see what direction we're going.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But it was not much we could see there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Everybody wanted to go there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we came-- we were stopped-- we were on the way about eight days.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we were stopped twice to stop to empty the buckets.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We couldn't empty ourself.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We had to do it in a bucket they left in the train.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And once they put us food in the wagon, and then we continued.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Of course, we did not-- we did not-- we did not drive straight to the-- to the camp.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Because from Italy to Poland, the maximum of 12 hours in a boxcar shouldn't take eight days.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "But there were much more important trains.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "We saw trains go rolling by with-- with British prisoners and German soldiers going to the front, while we were staying side tracked.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Sometimes we were standing there for all day.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And we arrived in a place that's called Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Birkenau, they opened the doors.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And we-- as soon as the door opened, we saw a lot of people, inmates, with stripes, clothes like pajamas.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And the came to us, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And they pushed us, pulled us out from the ride.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "We wanted to take our luggage.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "They said, [SPEAKING GERMAN] later, you know, you're going to get your luggage.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "So the women and men, everybody jumped down.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And the place was here, exactly where I'm standing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "We were disembarked here in this place.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
